# ========================================
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
*.p12
*.pfx

# ========================================
# REQUIRED FOR AWS AMPLIFY DEPLOYMENT
# ========================================
# The following files/directories ARE INCLUDED for deployment:
# - src/ (source code)
# - public/ (static assets)
# - package.json (dependencies)
# - pnpm-lock.yaml (lock file)
# - next.config.ts (Next.js configuration)
# - tsconfig.json (TypeScript configuration)
# - tailwind.config.js (if exists)
# - postcss.config.mjs (PostCSS configuration)
# - components.json (shadcn/ui configuration)
# - amplify.yml (Amplify build specification)
# - README.md (documentation)
# - DEPLOYMENT.md (deployment guide)
# - API_DOCUMENTATION.md (API reference)

# ========================================
# Optional: Development & Testing Scripts
# ========================================
# Uncomment if you don't want test scripts in production
test-*.sh
*.test.js
*.test.ts
*.spec.js
*.spec.ts
